	<h1 class="title">如果你不是好莱坞顶级编剧，老了你赚得也不会多</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/130051/small/130051.jpg?1435571000" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">温欣语 孙今泾</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-10 15:41:23 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11929/medium/11929.jpg?1436635565" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


